    <h1>Hood</h1><div id="preamble">
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The market Hood.de is only available in German. List your items as auctions, set up fixed price offers or sell items in your own store. With plentymarkets, you have full access to Hood. Learn how to list your items, set up your Hood store and edit your listings. The checkout process is done in your plentymarkets system.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
<h2 id="100">1. Registering with Hood</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>First register with <a href="https://www.hood.de/kostenlos-registrieren.htm?sec=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Hood</strong></a>. Create an API password, which you will need when setting up the interface to Hood in plentymarkets.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
<h2 id="200">2. Setting up Hood in plentymarkets</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Carry out the following steps in order to activate Hood in plentymarkets.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Entering Hood access data:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>System » Markets » Hood</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Pay attention to the explanations given in table 1 and enter the access data accordingly.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
