</td>
<td class="content">
<div class="title">Hood does not allow HTML tags in the short description of "store item" listings</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>HTML tags are not taken into consideration when transmitting the short description for Hood listings of the type <strong>Store item</strong>. This is because Hood does not support such HTML tags. The item’s <strong>Preview text</strong> is transferred from plentymarkets to Hood as the short description. This text is found by opening the item in the <strong>Item » Edit item</strong> menu and clicking on the <strong>Texts</strong> tab. Existing HTML tags are deleted and only plain text is transferred. <br>
HTML tags are permitted in the actual listing description.</p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
