<h2 id="5100">13. Automatically exchanging data</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Use the SOAP API or the <strong>Data exchange</strong> menu to exchange data between your plentymarkets system and Hood. The data format <strong>ItemListingMarketHood</strong> is used to create new Hood listings or edit existing listings, e.g. to change or delete parameters.</p>
</div>
